metadata.name: ARTEMIS CHOLL [AX008]
metadata.description:
After exploring the parallel worlds, Lady Sativa brought back the body of a female warrior. The ripped wings and a ravaged body but in her hand, she still held her weapon tightly. The brave heart was shown until the last moment. So she was rebuilt again and became AXANA's newest crew member, "ARTEMIS CHOLL" AX008

Created by AXANA
